IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. INTEGRATION.

DATA DIVISION.
01 MYVAR PICTURE IS 9(5).
01 COUNTER PICTURE IS 9.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "START EVALUATION"
    MOVE 10 TO MYVAR
    ADD 5 TO MYVAR GIVING MYVAR
    IF MYVAR > 10 THEN
        DISPLAY "GREATER"
    END
    LOOP VARYING COUNTER FROM 1 TO 5 BY 1
        DISPLAY COUNTER
    END
    STOP